以前，虽然比不上那些大佬，但也算是一小群人中的佼佼者。</p>\n<p>可现在，只是个小小职员，上也上不去，跳也不好跳，还要整天担心被裁员。</p>\n<p>如果那年，我没有乱跳槽，现在也不至于这样啊。</p>\n<p>如果那年，在「爱我的」和「我爱的」两个女孩中间，我没有选择后者，现在小孩估计都能跑了，那可是一个在我没车没房没存款的时候，不要彩礼还愿意跟我一起打拼攒钱买房的好女孩啊。。。</p>\n<p>可惜，人生没有如果，再也遇不到那个贵人，再也遇不到那个女孩...</p>\n<p>不再去想如果了...</p>\n<p>好在，自己父母健康，自己这份工作暂时还没丢，自己还有一点点积蓄，自己还有一点点梦想。</p>\n<p>趁梦想还没丢，趁自己还没放弃，继续努力吧，再拼一把。</p>\n<p>干中学，学中干，加油，自己。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1740711376, "replies": 219, "id": 1114780}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a4a0/42cf/171_large.png?m=1630576706", "name": "invest", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a4a0/42cf/171_normal.png?m=1630576706", "title": "投资", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/invest", "topics": 2257, "footer": "", "header": "Can you make money with money?", "title_alternative": "Invest", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a4a0/42cf/171_mini.png?m=1630576706", "stars": 3350, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 171, "parent_node_name": "money"}, "member": {"id": 665942, "username": "huhu222", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/huhu222", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/daf81dd1986731b328ef99bfbe1ef742?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/daf81dd1986731b328ef99bfbe1ef742?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/daf81dd1986731b328ef99bfbe1ef742?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1701855283, "last_modified": 1701855283}, "last_reply_by": "LanhuaMa", "last_touched": 1740765746, "title": "没人聊聊最近的纳指吗? 跌麻了", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1114779", "created": 1740704583, "deleted": 0, "content": "", "content_rendered": "", "last_modified": 1740711337, "replies": 130, "id": 1114779}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/38af/8613/176_large.png?m=1644885960", "name": "car", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/38af/8613/176_normal.png?m=1644885960", "title": "汽车", "url": "h